screen_desc: The screenshot shows a "Settings" page of an application. At the top, there is a profile section with a placeholder profile picture, the name "Ethan Do," a phone number, and an email address. Below the profile section, there are various "App Settings" options including "Add Home," "Add Work," "Shortcuts," "Privacy," "Appearance," and "Communication." Each option has an icon and a brief description. The "Safety" section is partially visible at the bottom. The time displayed at the top of the screen is 2:45 PM, and there are various status icons for notifications, battery, and network connectivity.
